title: Fixed crash
message:
Fixed crash

Before Android 4.1, method android.graphics.PorterDuffColorFilter
    android.support.graphics.drawable.VectorDrawableCompat.updateTintFilter(android.graphics.PorterDuffColorFilter,
    android.content.res.ColorStateList, android.graphics.PorterDuff$Mode)
    would have incorrectly overridden the package-private method in android.graphics.drawable.Drawable
    AppCompatViewInflater  I  app:theme is now deprecated. Please move to using android:theme instead.

title: Unauthorized: when 1st mobile devices signs in, user name (email) and user id…
message:
Unauthorized: when 1st mobile devices signs in, user name (email) and user id gets recorder into shared prefs.
Suppose 2 devices have signed in, and both of them have recorder data into shared prefs. Then the 1st one loggs out,
and the second one restarts the Chat - it get Unauthorized while attempting to send a message. Chat should jump to Login state.
